<item rdf:about="http://www.deitte.com/travel/archives/2006/06/picture_titles.html">
<title>Picture Titles and Descriptions</title>
<link>http://www.deitte.com/travel/archives/2006/06/picture_titles.html</link>
<description><![CDATA[<p>I've added titles and descriptions to some of the pictures found here:</p>

<p><A HREF="http://www.flickr.com/photos/bdeitte/sets/72157594144810446/">Bombay</A><br />
<A HREF="http://www.flickr.com/photos/bdeitte/sets/72157594144830027/">Delhi, Agra, Jaipur</A><br />
